Dear Sir/Madam,

Greetings !

We are pleased to present a 2 - days Management Development Programme
for Working professionals.

Programme Name
Selling Value: Moving Beyond Features and Benefits

Date
21st and 22nd June 2019 (Fri & Sat)

Location
SPJIMR Campus, Mumbai

Professor
Dr. Ranjan Banerjee & Prof. Veera Dikshit

Methodology
Group Interaction, Role plays, Classroom discussion, Case study

Price
Rs.25,000/- + GST

You may reserve your seats and avail early bird (1st 5 entries) and
Group discounts by replying to this email along with your contact
details at the earliest.

*Programme Objective :*

The course is designed to create best-in-breed sales professionals who
excel at creating value for their customers and organisation and move
up the value chain to being a “vendor” to a “trusted partner”.
Hence the programme aims to provide a comprehensive understanding of
the key concepts and time tested approaches towards the complex task
of Solution Selling, which is completely practice – oriented, skill
based learning; through a combination of case studies, role-plays and
live industry examples.

You may reply with you interest for registrations and discount and we
shall send the programme brochure and nomination form, please write to
