*About S.P. Jain Institute of Management and Research (SPJIMR)*

SPJIMR, a leading school of Management in the heart of India`s
financial capital, Mumbai with another centre in Delhi, has grown over
the years to be recognised as one of the top 6 business schools of
India. We are a part of Bharatiya Vidya Bhavan and function as an
autonomous institute with entrepreneurial agility.

SPJIMR has highly acclaimed Management Development Programme(MDP)
centre focused on key business fundamentals especially designed for
mid-senior level executives. It readies participants to take on
increasing executive responsibilities, broadens their knowledge and
prepares them to act. Last year we conducted 130 days of MDP for 138
unique companies namely Bosch, Hexaware, Reliance Industries,
Fresenius Kabi, YES Bank, Tata AIG General Insurance, National Stock
Exchange of India Ltd, Lucas-TVS Limited and many others.


